  {
    "id": "session-33-caw_summary",
    "type": "text",
    "props": {
      "content": "Descended from the Vanapur Mountains toward Khagdaruhel, the party were still commited to geting the dwarves support and they wanted to investigate rumors of the Cold Breath's growing influence on the Rimestone. Along the way they encountered the Sacred Crows, a capable adventuring group, who had been stalled outside Khagdaruhel searching for a missing blind goat beloved by a dwarven knight. The two parties formed a temporary alliance, tracked the goat to a foul cave occupied by an elder ettin. Dispatching the giant, they pressed deeper to discover ancient dwarven towers now held by drow bearing banners of fangs and webs. In a coordinated assault on the towers, the combined force battled through the drow and a venomous spider-like boss that webbed and struck from the shadows.",
