      "rowSpan": "1"
    }
  },
  {
    "id": "session-32-over-the-edge_summary",
    "type": "text",
    "props": {
      "content": "The group was in a dwarven tomb the Vanapur Mountains that have been claimed by Presagiath. After battling a fiery copper dwarven construct guardian in an ancient tomb and climbing a hidden spiral staircase into her frozen cavern, they were ambushed by the dragon, who had been clinging unseen to the ceiling. A brutal fight unfolded atop a sheer cliff edge, with Presagiath's chilling breath, grapples, and near-fatal drops nearly wiping the group; several members. Pagern delivered the killing firebolt that sent the dragon plummeting to her death, allowing the battered survivors to claim a vast hoard of coin, gems, art objects, and powerful magic items.",
      "col": "1",
      "row": "15",
      "colSpan": "1",
      "rowSpan": "1"
    }
  },
