  {
    "id": "session-30-let-s-break-a-deal_summary",
    "type": "text",
    "props": {
      "content": "The party set out to confront the consequences of their bargain with the hags and decide whether to uphold or break the deal entirely. The situation escalated when a warning vision revealed the growing threat of Coldbreath, after which the party turned on their hag escort and fought to end the pact by force. The battle was brutal and costly, ending with the hag's death but leaving Lucerion maimed when he lost an arm to corrosive magic. The party then faced Madam Mabel, completed the exchange on altered terms, and watched her restore her youth, before regrouping and moving on under the weight of new power, new scars, and far-reaching consequences.",
