  {
    "id": "session-29-hags-with-bags_summary",
    "type": "text",
    "props": {
      "content": "The party set out to repay a dangerous favor owed to Madam Mabel by stepping through a Fey-touched gateway and retrieving specific items from the strange locals beyond it. Their journey quickly escalated, forcing them to fight off an orc warband, navigate a hostile and watchful mine, and confront warped fey creatures. The task culminated in a brutal clash with three disguised hags, a fight that drained the party but revealed the true nature of their opposition. Rather than ending in simple victory, the session closed with a tense negotiation with a more powerful hag, leaving the party bound by a precarious bargain and facing far more complicated consequences.",
